snippet.title: Mini Airways Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Mini Airways Demo is available on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2289650/Mini_Airways/

As an air traffic controller, you'll oversee flight takeoffs and landings. ✈️  Upgrade terminals, expand flight zones, and more to optimize airspace efficiency.
But that's not all—be prepared to handle unexpected events anytime!  Can you become the best ATC ever? 😏 

Join Discord: https://discord.gg/QtxwBzXnA7
